ActBoards of Trade Act
SubjectChambre de commerce et d'industrie Magog-Orford (Quebec) ** Change of Boundaries **
PrecisOrder approving the application by the CHAMBRE DE COMMERCE ET D'INDUSTRIE DE MAGOG-ORFORD, in Quebec, to CHANGE THE BOUNDARIES OF ITS DISTRICT, namely the City and the Township of Magog, to Austin, Ayer's Cliff, Bolton-Est, Eastman, Hatley, Township of Hatley, Ogden, Township of Orford, Township of Potton, Saint-Benoît-du-Lac, Sainte-Étenne-de-Bolton, Sainte-Catherine-de-Hatley, Township of Stanstead, Town of Stanstead et Village of Stukely-Sud.
